			0.8 version
			-------------
incompatibility : 
* the log format was changed (previous log will not work with this release)
* default behavior is to work on all attributes

bugfix : 
* rollback was fixed

new features :
* can use rcfile
* recode rollback to use options (batch, dryrun, attributes choice)
